OL,3,C'Dementia-village' care home opens
OL,4,Cwhere 'independence is primary'
OL,6,FThe first dementia care home, based on
OL,7,Fa Dutch model, where the facility is
OL,8,Fdesigned as a village, has opened in
OL,9,Fthe South.
OL,11,FNorden House in Littlehampton, West
OL,12,FSussex, hopes to ease the transition
OL,13,Ffor residents going from their home
OL,14,Finto care and provide them with
OL,15,Findependence.
OL,17,FOn-site there is a hairdresser, where
OL,18,Fresidents can have weekly
OL,19,Fappointments, there is a cafe, where
OL,20,Fthey can eat with visiting family
OL,21,Fmembers, and a garden to plant flowers.
