OL,3,C'Dementia-village' care home opens
OL,4,Cwhere 'independence is primary'
OL,6,FHealthcare Management Trust, Mair
OL,7,FWilliams said: "Coming into a care
OL,8,Fhome is overwhelming for the family
OL,9,Fand the individual.
OL,11,F"What we have here, is a domestic-
OL,12,Fscale hub, or household, in which care
OL,13,Fis delivered and independence is
OL,14,Fprimary in supporting those
OL,15,Findividuals."
OL,17,FWeekly costs start from #1,600 per
OL,18,Fperson for residential care at Norden
OL,19,FHouse, which the Trust says is
OL,20,F"comparable" to other care homes.
