OL,3,C'Dementia-village' care home opens
OL,4,Cwhere 'independence is primary'
OL,6,F87-year-old Anne Bevan, resident of
OL,7,FNorden House, said: "All the people
OL,8,Fare really lovely, never cross, they
OL,9,Fmight be when they go out the door!
OL,11,F"It's a good job there are people like
OL,12,Fthat to look after us."
OL,14,FAnne's daughters, Sue Alexander and
OL,15,FJackie Dyall spoke to ITV News
OL,16,FMeridian saying: "It's a huge
OL,17,Fdecision, a massive decision, a
OL,18,Fdifficult decision.
